{"tid":801551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「純發洩」有個自大、自戀、完美主意、雙重標準嘅兄弟 真係好撚辛苦","createTime":"2018-08-31T17:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T01:44:17.000Z","uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23fd7353693de17c96c263e50263d997f802a2aa","tid":801551,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"哩個兄弟人緣好好，好易留比新相識嘅人一個好印象<br />\n<br />\n「外向、風趣、有自信、熱情」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一直都好好奇點解佢身邊咁多朋友，但係好似仲一事無成咁，所以多左去了解佢。<br />\n<br />\n唔行近由自可，一行近就出事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同佢去兩日三夜（原本可以係三日三夜）旅行，兩丁友去嘅，未去我就開始feel到瀨瀨地野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為大家都唔想洗太多錢，所以坐長途火車。訂車票嗰時就同我講，星期六晚要去玩，會玩好夜，叫我唔好搵星期六夜晚車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌佢，我心諗，哂一日時間坐車，十鳩幾個鐘呀你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都算，我搵d野係車做算，所以訂左星期日朝早車<br />\n<br />\n到訂房，你個閪，又要gym房又要游泳池又要市中心又要平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是撚但，佢自己簡飽佢<br />\n<br />\n到起程嗰日，去到車站問鳩我有冇床，我話冇，叫佢問下有冇得upgrade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗，你個閪9成都唔會有啦下化，中間咁撚多個站<br />\n不出所料，真係冇，要夜晚車先有<br />\n上到車姨姨鵝鵝，話坐得唔舒服訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇，到差唔多落車，我啱啱訓醒，問佢係咪到喇，佢話係，咁咪落車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌佢，早左一個站，都算，我都有責任<br />\n佢又唔趕路，掛住影相，掛住搵野食，過左時間除時過唔到關咖，又唔係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇，影完買完野食，打的去目的地，過關嘅時候要比錢做落地簽證，佢問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指住張表叫佢睇下，佢叫我收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 屌你大帝咩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又姨姨鵝鵝話的士貴，又話我做咩唔住實，成日慢三拍<br />\n你老味，你攪你d野就得，我行慢兩步就有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到酒店成夜晚9點，咁就冇左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好撚柒閪多，但唔想篇文太長<br />\n有人想知先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adee3edde8d18aff255a7f7cdcaeea3bad2ab3f1","tid":801551,"uid":78622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"Tldr"},{"pid":"73570a4a4b866e889a0cfd963f0afa93b100b978","tid":801551,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23fd7353693de17c96c263e50263d997f802a2aa","tid":801551,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"哩個兄弟人緣好好，好易留比新相識嘅人一個好印象<br />\n<br />\n「外向、風趣、有自信、熱情」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 